# Database

- Migrations are **sequential** and **global** (not per-agent parallel files) — Infra/Foundation coordinates order.
- Every tenant-scoped table includes `tenant_id` when multi-tenant model applies.
- Document new tables/columns in the relevant module contract when behavior is user-visible.
